import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import 'antd/dist/antd.css';
import './App.css';
import { Layout, Menu, Breadcrumb } from 'antd';
import { Button } from 'antd';

import { Avatar, Image } from 'antd';
import { Badge, Space, Switch } from 'antd';
import {
    DesktopOutlined,
    PieChartOutlined,
    FileOutlined,
    TeamOutlined,
    UserOutlined,
} from '@ant-design/icons';

const { Header, Content, Footer, Sider } = Layout;
const { SubMenu } = Menu;

                      <Row style={{ display: 'inline-flex', justifyContent: 'center'}} gutter={[16, 16]} >

                          <Col>

                          <Col >

                      <Row style={{ display: 'inline-flex', justifyContent: 'center'}} gutter={[16, 16]} >
                          <Col >

                      </Row>

              </Menu>
          </Layout>
          <Layout theme="dark" >
              <Row  theme="dark"  style={{ display: 'inline-flex', justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                  <Col>
                      <Button>Up</Button>
                  </Col>
                  <Col>
                      <Button>Down</Button>
                  </Col>
              </Row>

          </Layout>
          <Footer style={{ display: 'inline-flex', justifyContent: 'center'}}>
              Tobi Pizda
          </Footer>
      </Layout>
  );
}

export default App;
